metadata.name: Harper 1/1
metadata.description:
Accurate rendition of self-articulated high skill tendencies. Mythological representations of known events placed into monogrammed fabric. Constructed practice through attitude. Mustard pink lemonade multi-pocket bomber racer jacket, sewed graphic labels and patches. 

Synth Graph: real life full photograph of a beautiful pink haired tanned 25 year old female posing with luxury fashion streetwear, wearing an oversized Racing Bomber Jacket in Black, captured with a Nikon D7100, high resolution, very detailed, highly realistic. Sampler: klms, steps: 70, scale: 10.
